Welcome to Bonus Joker!

Goal of the game:
The objective of the game is to spin the 3 reels to get 3 identical symbols in at least one of the paylines. In the bonus game, winnings are added for each JOKER symbol individually. Depending on the symbols obtained in the payline and the paytable, the winnings are added to the credit. The game has 5 paylines.

BONUS symbol:
3 or more BONUS symbols placed at least one from 5 winning lines starts BONUS game with free spins. The number of free spins for the BONUS game is 5 to 10 free spins for each line with 3 BONUS symbols.

JOKER symbol:
The JOKER symbol can replace any other symbol.

Controls  Buttons:
START  Places the bet and spins the reels.
AUTO START  Turns automatic bets on or off.
AUTO START  Can be activated by holding the START button.

and   Increases or decreases the active bet. The bet can be changed by clicking in the Bet field or on the Finance tab.

Additional Information:
Malfunction voids all plays and pays.

Only the highest combination of symbols is paid.
The values shown on paytable are depending on currently selected bet value.

JACKPOTS:
This game participates in mystery jackpot. The prize in each level is awarded when a random win point is reached. Mystery jackpot cannot be gambled on.
